Description: Single-cell datasets are growing in size rapidly, posing challenges as well as opportunities for biology researchers. ondisc (short for “on-disk single cell”) is a package that empowers users to easily and efficiently analyze large-scale single-cell data. ondisc makes computing on large-scale single-cell data FUN: Fast, Universal, and Ntuitive.
